sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant R as React UI
    participant F as FastAPI Router
    participant S as TaskService
    participant D as SQLite

    U->>R: Fill form and click "Create Task"
    R->>R: Optimistically add pending task to list
    R->>F: POST /tasks (JSON payload)

    F->>F: Validate request body
    F->>S: create_task(data)

    S->>D: INSERT INTO tasks (...)
    D-->>S: Return new row (id, timestamps, fields)

    S-->>F: Created task DTO
    F-->>R: 201 Created + created task (JSON)

    R->>R: Reconcile optimistic item with server task
    R-->>U: Show new task in list (saved)
